name: igawa asagi (井河 アサギ) from taimanin (対魔忍)
description:
This is my first lora, and I have to say it's a lot better than I expected!

I am a big fan of taimanin, and asagi is one of my favorite character ever! which is why I uploaded this Lora.

I recommend using a strength between 0.4-0.8, 1.0 is a bit too high.

Hope you enjoy this lora and have fun!

About the katana, it always goes wrong and I don't know how to fix it.

Changelog:

V2:

- reduce strength

- retraining lora

modelVersions.description: Now it works perfectly with abyssorangemix2_nsfw, perfectworld, chilloutmix and Grapefruit hentai model! Praise the machine god!
